name: SIWCMS
tagline: Semantic Interface for Web Content Management Systems
body:
### Semantify your CMS!
SIWCMS allows developers to create their semantic interfaces to interact with various RESTful semantic engines.
### External Libraries
This project utilizes EasyRDF, php-sql-to-sparql and Httpful libraries. Licence information of these libraries can be found in their websites.
